    "name": "Foul Bliss",
    "steam_appid": 3223180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/8e9f0b1b8fa140967826d51e5e5231b2.avif?t=1747040830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras_big/8e9f0b1b8fa140967826d51e5e5231b2.avif?t=1747040830 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Foul Bliss</strong> is a story-driven psychological horror game—a surreal tale about cinema, music, and the coexistence of beauty and terror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of an 80s movie protagonist, complete with a film grain effect, and immerse yourself in the atmosphere with an original soundtrack. Explore an old mansion hidden in a foggy forest and meet its inhabitants. Follow the instructions of a voice on the radio and survive in a world teetering between art and reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/f1fe31ef1035a09fd8c597900f67e2df.poster.avif?t=1747040830\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/f1fe31ef1035a09fd8c597900f67e2df.webm?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/f1fe31ef1035a09fd8c597900f67e2df.mp4?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/193204da19750438d3bf7f73d96b7665.avif?t=1747040830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras_big/193204da19750438d3bf7f73d96b7665.avif?t=1747040830 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player is not helpless—they have the means to defend themselves, but weapons require skillful handling and careful ammo management. There are no unlimited bullets here, and every pull of the trigger must be a deliberate choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/c7b19c4d2f3275ee35cd68578f049db4.poster.avif?t=1747040830\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/c7b19c4d2f3275ee35cd68578f049db4.webm?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/e12d014b255345c6f09d7fa5cca88316.avif?t=1747040830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras_big/e12d014b255345c6f09d7fa5cca88316.avif?t=1747040830 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark story that immerses players in a surreal world where cinema, music, and the darker aspects of the human psyche intertwine. This is a game for those who appreciate layered narratives and tension that steadily builds with every detail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/08a4934b7fa1c9f4d455da3ec60006cc.poster.avif?t=1747040830\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/08a4934b7fa1c9f4d455da3ec60006cc.webm?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/08a4934b7fa1c9f4d455da3ec60006cc.mp4?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/a9133e4dc3481abbfd3b70d3f7cbac4a.avif?t=1747040830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras_big/a9133e4dc3481abbfd3b70d3f7cbac4a.avif?t=1747040830 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A specially crafted original soundtrack accompanies every moment of the game, enhancing the atmosphere and capturing the balance between beauty and fear. The music accentuates emotional moments and adds depth to the narrative, helping players fully immerse themselves in the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/d5aece91d87ddb74cd8ab7fc8e52319a.avif?t=1747040830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras_big/d5aece91d87ddb74cd8ab7fc8e52319a.avif?t=1747040830 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player receives instructions through a radio, following the guidance of a mysterious voice. This adds intrigue to the game, as the voice can either help or mislead, and the motives of whoever is behind it remain unclear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/c2ed631b16fe9fe66a4b7cc3c227bab6.poster.avif?t=1747040830\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/c2ed631b16fe9fe66a4b7cc3c227bab6.webm?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/c2ed631b16fe9fe66a4b7cc3c227bab6.mp4?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/6e03f25dcfa14ce20d20fbb34d65b4a4.avif?t=1747040830\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras_big/6e03f25dcfa14ce20d20fbb34d65b4a4.avif?t=1747040830 width=800 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Foul Bliss</strong>, the boundaries of reality are blurred—the mansion is not just a place but a gateway to something beyond this world. A realm of nightmarish visions, where every second spent within it alters reality and its inhabitants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/9e9545f6231f150770450acc2151021c.poster.avif?t=1747040830\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/9e9545f6231f150770450acc2151021c.webm?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223180/extras/9e9545f6231f150770450acc2151021c.mp4?t=1747040830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
